 * |  6  4  2  |                
 *  \_5__3__1_/                 |  color codes
 *                              |  (cheap cable from eBay)
 * 2 = SO (serial output)       |  BROWN
 * 3 = SI (serial input)        |  GREEN
 * 5 = SC (serial clock)        |  BLUE
 * 6 = GND                      |  RED
